Lukaisu Server
==============

Lukaisu Server is the self-hosted backend for the Lukaisu reading app
(https://github.com/lukaisu/lukaisu).

Attribution / provenance
------------------------

Lukaisu Server is a fork derived from "Learning with Texts" (LWT) at version
3.2.0:

  - Immediate upstream: Learning with Texts (LWT), community-maintained by
    HugoFara and contributors — https://github.com/HugoFara/lwt
  - Original work: "Learning with Texts" by lang-learn-guy, first released in
    2011 — https://sourceforge.net/projects/learning-with-texts

The project was rebranded from LWT to Lukaisu Server throughout (PHP namespace,
package identity, runtime keys, assets, and documentation). The functional code
at the 0.1.0 baseline corresponds to LWT 3.2.0.

